The '''extinct Shola species''' were a unique race originally native to [[Shola/Legends|Shola]]. They presumably had a rather advanced society, in that the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] had [[Mining/Legends|mines]] and tunnels extending nearly to the core itself. However, they were wiped out along with their [[City/Legends|cities]], when the planet was [[Destruction of Shola|ravaged]]. It was theorized that it was their own doings that caused the scarring of their planet. These people left behind ruins.

